election_record.label: Connecticut 1819 State Senate

overview.note: Chauncey Willors is listed as a candidate in the Original Election Returns but is not listed with any votes.

sub_unit.name: New Fairfield
sub_unit.note: There were no votes recorded in New Fairfield.

sub_unit.name: Wilton
sub_unit.note: Jonathan W. Edwards received 79 votes as Jonathan Edwards.

sub_unit.name: Suffield
sub_unit.note: John S. Peters received 257 votes as John I. Peters.

sub_unit.name: East Haven
sub_unit.note: The votes for Calvin Goddard were not included in the Original Election Returns as "the presiding officer omitted to return."
